                    </span>
                </div>
                
                <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl font-extrabold leading-tight text-white max-w-4xl drop-shadow-lg">
                    TÃº creas la <span class="gradient-text">marca</span>, <br class="hidden md:block"/> nosotros ponemos <span class="text-primary underline decoration-4 underline-offset-8 decoration-white/30">la Plataforma</span>.
                </h1>
                
                <div class="text-base md:text-lg text-slate-100 max-w-lg leading-relaxed backdrop-blur-md bg-white/10 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-white/10 shadow-2xl">
                    <p>
                        <span class="font-bold text-xl md:text-2xl block mb-2 text-white">ðŸš€ Oportunidad Ãºnica:</span>
                        Estamos buscando a los <strong class="text-white">primeros 300 emprendedores</strong> para transformar el comercio en Colombia.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 pt-4">
                    <a href="#registro" class="bg-primary text-white text-center px-8 py-4 rounded-full text-lg font-bold hover:scale-105 transition-all shadow-xl shadow-primary/30 hover:shadow-primary/50 no-underline inline-flex items-center justify-center">
                        Unirme al Club de Pioneros
                        <span class="material-icons-round ml-2">arrow_forward</span>
                    </a>
                    <a href="#pilares" class="bg-white/10 text-white border border-white/30 backdrop-blur-md px-8 py-4 rounded-full text-lg font-bold text-center hover:bg-white/20 hover:scale-105 transition-all no-underline">
                        Ver beneficios
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="wave-divider">
        <svg class="fill-white dark:fill-background-dark transition-colors duration-500" preserveAspectRatio="none" viewBox="0 0 1200 120">
            <path d="M321.39,56.44c58-10.79,114.16-30.13,172-41.86,82.39-16.72,168.19-17.73,250.45-.39C823.78,31,906.67,72,985.66,92.83c70.05,18.48,146.53,26.09,214.34,3V120H0V0C49.1,13.84,105.7,35.34,166,49.19,203.76,57.84,263.82,64.21,321.39,56.44Z"></path>
        </svg>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    /* Clases de apoyo especÃ­ficas */
    .hero-gradient {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(45, 27, 105, 0.95) 0%, rgba(230, 0, 126, 0.6) 100%);
    }

    .wave-divider {
        position: absolute;
        bottom: 0;
        left: 0;
        width: 100%;
        overflow: hidden;
        line-height: 0;
        z-index: 50;
    }

    .wave-divider svg {
        position: relative;
        display: block;
        width: calc(150% + 1.3px);
        height: 80px;
    }

    @keyframes fade-in {
        from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(10px); }
        to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    }

    .animate-fade-in {
        animation: fade-in 1s ease-out forwards;
    }
</style>